{"id": 448, "genre": 1000, "title": "如何运动让你更像一个中产阶级？", "description": "人是铁，范儿是钢，一天不装憋得慌。对于中产阶级这个可爱的群体，我们充满了爱意。好奇心研究所会不定期推出紧跟时代节奏的“中产阶级装腔指南”，和大家一起分享研究生活的心得。", "record_count": 1555, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071946517eHOB94kCPyq8oLh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-27T17:22:33Z", "questions": [{"id": 349, "title": "如何运动让你更像一个中产阶级？", "content": "中产阶级如何运动？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 5769, "content": "跑鞋一定要避震次顶级或者赤足系列跑鞋", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193910NRbMzanY8AwhQFj1.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 5770, "content": "听音乐不能把手机攥手里，要用个臂带啥的", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193142f81ANjz9cE6Q4hak.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 5771, "content": "一定要偏爱拳击，棒球这种小众运动", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193720J952fFsGRk4cPY7b.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 5772, "content": "私教要提前预约按小时收费的那种", "image": "img/option/option/20160607194038j4wQD7qtI0fYiBSh.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 5773, "content": "喜欢登山，溯溪等接触大自然的运动", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193820a1JECBpU26dmZYnv.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 5774, "content": "非常重视心率、卡路里及记录这些数值的手环", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193142QNcXFhuHyO3KS19n.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 5775, "content": "一定要晒运动路线，可爱的10公里！", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193925lhfYownEOrWQJe2d.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 5776, "content": "运动后必然搭配营养师建议的营养套餐", "image": "img/option/option/201606071931423GmoBjCdsPfJixHE.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}